rooms.Name: The Arena
rooms.Description:
Welcome to the Arena of Death.  Here, assassins can happily hack each other
to death without stepping on anybody's toes.  This area is home to several
warriors, and finding them will improve your chance for survival.  Please,
no newbies should be here, for your sake.
Have fun and kill each other!!!

rooms.Name: The Arena Quest Ring Out
rooms.Description:
You have stepped out of bounds.  For doing so you have lost this round to you
opponent.
